For someone who probably has lots of INT, your statement belies that fact.<br>
<br>
You must also function in groups of 3.  The other 3?  Add two more melee damage dealers and a Bard for Slow/Haste/DS/STR etc. and the overall DPS of that group will skyrocket.  Not to mention the DPS that Charmed Mobs can do.<br>
<br>
Now that I think about it, your 3 person group is flawed.  Tank, Healer, CROWD CONTROL (a role that Bards do quite nicely when they know what they are doing!).  It is the Damage Dealer (Wizard) that is not needed.  Cleric keeps the Warrior healed up, and the Chanter makes sure he takes em one at a time.  I'm afraid that Wizards are just as much an &quot;extra&quot; to a &quot;perfect&quot; (read BORING) group as a Bard is.<br>
<br>
btw, when was the last time that EQ was FUN for you?<br>
